    "time_stamp": "2023-08-28 14:15:03",
    "text": "To use fonts that HubSpot doesn't provide, the email needs to be custom coded. HubSpot's email builder is limited to the font families available in the drop down. See here under Email: <https://knowledge.HubSpot.com/website-pages/use-fonts-in-HubSpot>"
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Jillian McGuire",
      "poster_handle": "jmcguire"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2023-08-28 14:18:36",
    "text": "Thank you, Courtney! Do you happen to know if HubSpot has a list of email developers they recommend?"
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Courtney Fantinato",
      "poster_handle": "courtneyfantinato"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2023-08-28 14:25:51",
    "text": "Partners directory <https://ecosystem.HubSpot.com/marketplace/solutions|https://ecosystem.HubSpot.com/marketplace/solutions>\n\nYou may also be able to find someone in <#CBNDYJJAZ|jobs> "
  },
  {
    "poster": {
