  {
    "text": "How would you approach recreating this email template in HubSpot's Drag-and-Drop email template builder? Is it possible? Simple email but not straightforward to replicate.\n\nChallenging aspects are:\n• The dark background overhang\n• The white content area rounded corners\n• The dark background that expands beyond 600px width content area",
